Gottheil is a good lecturer, ignore the tongue clicks.  Do the homeworks, as the exams are similar to them.  Find a TA who speaks English well, as Gottheil is not known for his zeal in working with undergrads.  Quizzes are easy, as long as you attend class and do the readings.  The key is to practice with the homeworks.  I got a B in the class.
